{
  "stem": "13690.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You are actually the owner of the house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I refuse you?'",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, 'That's nice of you.' So my mother even said not the question of no.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was plenty Jewish homes that they were empty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they were not this nice as this one, but there were.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we moved in into the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Eli, of course, went out to school to [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Lodz, ?] to the second largest city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I stayed there with my mother, and my uncle, and aunt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then in May, my brother and sister, they already left Poland, and I remained with my mother in the town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Seemingly, they were told that they-- under false papers, under illegal way, they would be able to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They set out for Palestine, but they got stuck in Germany.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I tried to do is, being a young boy, I tried to register to school.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But somehow, somewhere, there was a reluctance to-- to be accepted even to-- to finish my public, or to go to high school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was not welcome.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was not welcome to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It happened to be that I was the one that my father took me to-- to show where he is hiding.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he-- I mean, relatively speaking, going back today, living today in America, it's-- what means money?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it's so relative to say how much means money money?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in those days, I felt my father was hiding boxes of gold, I mean, and coins, and all kind of precious things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that was the main reason why my mother wanted to put the foot in the door and to be able to get into the house.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
